<P>
   &UR; FED _ &LR;  Trying yet again to pour cold water on the red-hot U.S.
economy, the Federal Reserve raised short-term interest rates to a
nine-year high Tuesday and signaled loud and clear that further
increases may be in the works.  &UR; BY DAVID LAZARUS &LR;
