<HEADLINE>
SMOKING: TINSELTOWN'S NASTY HABIT  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
   (This 675-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
 &HT;    
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
