   Since distribution, not paper or printing, is a publisher's
biggest cost, Stephen King may soon have some company on the
electronic bookshelf. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (EDITOR'S NOTE: Dave Califano is a staff writer at ``Worth.'') &LR;  &QL;   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; _______ &QC;
</P>
