<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GERMANY-REAGANOMICS-RESEND-WORTH-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
RETOOLING THE OLD `GERMAN MODEL' ECONOMY  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Business Editors...RESENDING from May 10)   (This 600-word ``separate-buy'' financial story is from ``WORTH''
magazine. To publish this article, it must be purchased from the
New York Times Syndicate's sales representative DEBRA WEYDERT at
