<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-17 13:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7629 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r f BC-AUTO-OFF-ROAD-HNS &LR;      05-17 1650
