<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are considering for
the Page 1 of Thursday, May 18. The N.Y. Times News Service night
supervisor is Ned Kilkelly; phone: (888) 346-9867; e-mail:
nekill(at)nytimes.com.
