   CHINA-TRADE (Washington) _ China trade legislation received the
endorsement Wednesday of four previously undecided Democrats in
Congress, indicating that the White House and congressional
supporters may be less than 10 votes shy of the number needed for
passage. By Eric Schmitt.
</P>
