   RUSSIA-OLIGARCHS (Moscow) _ Putin administration is taking shape
with confirmation of his prime minister and a surprise decision to
keep the prosecutor. Analysts see both as signs that President
Vladimyr Putin has no interest in bringing down the oligarchs or
challenging their power. By Brian Whitmore. 750 words.
</P>
