<P>
   LAPD-RAMPART (Los Angeles) _ City leaders meet with Feds on LAPD
reforms. By Beth Barrett. (Will move in the ``a'' national and
``n'' California news files.)
</P>
<P>
   CALIFORNIA-TECH (Los Angeles) _ California is the nation's
technology powerhouse, employing 835,000 workers in 1998. It was
also the fastest growing state between 1993 and 1998, creating
193,000 new high-tech jobs. And the pay here is pretty good, too,
averaging $66,900, third nationally, according to a study released
Wednesday. (Will move in the ``a'' national, ``f'' financial and
