last year concluded that privatization of the Galveston County
(Texas) employees' retirement plan benefited high-income employees
but hurt low-paid ones. Vice President Al Gore's campaign is
pointing to the study in its argument against the Social Security
investment accounts proposed by Republican George W. Bush. By
BENNETT ROTH.
