<HEADLINE>
ANIMATION EVOLVES BIGTIME IN `DINOSAUR'
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Fact box below) 
Our rating: 3 1/2 stars 
By BOB STRAUSS 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   While it is impossible to overpraise the visual splendor of
